#: templates/recommender.html:133
msgid ""
"This is a list of resources your fellow students thought might be helpful. "
"If you find another useful resource, either on edx.org or elsewhere, please "
"add it. If you can improve the description or preview of a resource, please "
"do so as well. If you find a resource helpful, upvote it. If it&rsquo;s not "
"so helpful, downvote it. If it has issues (illegal material, incorrect, "
"etc.), please flag it and let us know the reason."
msgstr ""
"Ini adalah daftar sumber daya yang dianggap bermanfaat oleh teman-teman "
"sekelas Anda. Jika Anda menemukan sumber daya lain yang berguna, baik di "
"edx.org maupun di tempat lain, silakan tambahkan. Jika Anda dapat "
"memperbaiki deskripsi atau pratinjau suatu sumber daya, silakan lakukan. "
"Jika Anda menemukan sumber daya yang bermanfaat, beri upvote. Jika tidak "
"begitu berguna, beri downvote. Jika ada masalah (materi ilegal, tidak benar,"
" dll.), silakan beri tanda dan beritahu kami alasannya."

